{"tid":2060741,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"西營盤中山紀念公園發生巨大火警，濃煙遠至尖沙咀可見","createTime":"2020-06-12T01:10:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-12T02:11:06.000Z","uid":149978,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f2514a5d702cd2c1db4fe1004cdfaaf8b5e2e964","tid":2060741,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T01:10:39.000Z","msg":"西營盤中山紀念公園今日（11日）下午5時許，有發泡膠箱起火冒煙，火勢猛烈，濃煙捲上半空，多名網民都於事發時拍下影片及照片，遠至對岸尖沙咀亦可見到濃濃黑煙。<br />\n<br />\n火警發生於西營盤海旁的中山紀念公園體育館，一堆放於路邊近花槽的發泡膠箱起火，並波及旁邊草堆，由於位置接近西隧，故有不少駕駛者都見到火警引起的黑煙，紛紛拍下影片和照片，甚至有人在對岸的尖沙咀海旁見到濃煙席捲半空。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1793815/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E4%B8%AD%E5%B1%B1%E7%B4%80%E5%BF%B5%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92%E7%99%BC%E6%B3%A1%E8%86%A0%E7%AE%B1%E8%B5%B7%E7%81%AB-%E6%BF%83%E7%85%99%E9%81%A0%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%96%E6%B2%99%E5%92%80%E5%8F%AF%E8%A6%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1793815%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E7%25B4%2580%25E5%25BF%25B5%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%259C%2592%25E7%2599%25BC%25E6%25B3%25A1%25E8%2586%25A0%25E7%25AE%25B1%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E7%2581%25AB-%25E6%25BF%2583%25E7%2585%2599%25E9%2581%25A0%25E8%2587%25B3%25E5%25B0%2596%25E6%25B2%2599%25E5%2592%2580%25E5%258F%25AF%25E8%25A6%258B&d=isL%2BTa9V4QtjyiE8eWWd0lKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=048b5dca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1793815%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E7%25B4%2580%25E5%25BF%25B5%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%259C%2592%25E7%2599%25BC%25E6%25B3%25A1%25E8%2586%25A0%25E7%25AE%25B1%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E7%2581%25AB-%25E6%25BF%2583%25E7%2585%2599%25E9%2581%25A0%25E8%2587%25B3%25E5%25B0%2596%25E6%25B2%2599%25E5%2592%2580%25E5%258F%25AF%25E8%25A6%258B&h=d77794f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/new